  &lt;li&gt;Troubleshooting, investigating, and creating detailed bug reports&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Crafting and editing helpful support documentation&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Being an active member of a team that provides around the clock support to our users via live chat, forums, and email&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Building a community of support by sharing knowledge and insight amongst team members&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Being a Happiness Engineer requires:&lt;/h2&gt;
